      "name": "FDA GCBP bench-to-CFD hemolysis comparison across 5 operating points",
      "description": "CFD-predicted RH values compared against in-vitro measurements for 5 flow-speed combinations. Mean RH = 0.87 (range 0.74–0.96). Comparison satisfies the upper-bound criterion (all RH < 1.0) but violates the equivalence floor criterion (no RH ≥ 1.0), exposing the mutual exclusivity of the two bound requirements."
