    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The package is accepted for regulatory submission. Note: the two bound acceptance requirements (RH upper-bound and RH equivalence floor) were treated as independently satisfied during review; their mutual exclusivity was not identified prior to submission.",
